name: [center]Jormungandr[/center]
text: ([color=#FF0000][i]WARRIOR[/i][/color], you may have besssted me, but it’s only a minor sssetback)

name: [center]Jormungandr[/center]
text: (Tell that coward to fight his own battlessss next time)

name: [center]Jormungandr[/center]
text: (If you’re the bessst they have, it won’t be long now…)
